    "zh-TW": "管理員角色概覽",
    "en": "Admin Role Overview"
  },
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": {
      "zh-TW": "管理員是知識庫的所有者或維護者。他們擁有所有貢獻者能力、直接寫入權限、批准或拒絕提案的能力、管理成員以及軟刪除和恢復工作區的能力。",
      "en": "Admins are repository owners or maintainers. They possess all contributor capabilities, direct write access, the ability to approve or reject proposals, manage members, and soft-delete and restore workspaces."
    }
  },
